text: @HillBeverlyhill @PhoenixGirl73 I have heard similar, attribution of COVID19 deaths to secondary effects or nominal prior existing conditions like COPD. But they were otherwise healthy or maintaining successfully with their conditions prior to the COVID19 infection. Bingo, uncounted COVID19 death.
